	&lt;p data-end=&quot;500&quot; data-start=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-end=&quot;406&quot; data-start=&quot;396&quot;&gt;Event:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong data-end=&quot;431&quot; data-start=&quot;407&quot;&gt;Saraswati Pushkaralu&lt;/strong&gt; (सरस्वति पुश्करलु) &amp;ndash; a &lt;strong data-end=&quot;475&quot; data-start=&quot;455&quot;&gt;once-in-12-years&lt;/strong&gt; mega religious festival.&lt;/p&gt;
